= Master Mindset: The Qualification Philosophy

#box(width: 100%, fill: rgb("#3D2314"), inset: 12pt, radius: 5pt)[
  #text(fill: white, size: 11pt, weight: "bold", style: "italic")[
    "Bờ không biết Bờ có giúp được bạn không" \
    (I don't know if I can help you)
  ]

  #v(0.2cm)

  #text(fill: rgb("#D4A853"), size: 8pt)[
    *The Master's Approach:* Like a martial arts master, I have my own rules and standards. I don't chase clients - I qualify them. Respect over revenue. Not everyone belongs here, and that's by design.

    *Prospect Products (£15-20):* GPT tools, chatbots, e-books, e-courses are NOT for revenue. They're filters. Only people who engage with these AND show seriousness get invited to 1-on-1 consultation.

    *1-on-1 Consultation:* Even after buying, they must qualify in conversation. Do they have the mindset? The commitment? The respect for the craft? If no → refund and move on.
  ]
]

